<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>阅读路线 - Tag - 堂堂一跑堂</title><link>https://spacetop.win/tags/%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF/</link><description>阅读路线 - Tag - 堂堂一跑堂</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><managingEditor>kingcopper@whu.edu.cn (WangTong)</managingEditor><webMaster>kingcopper@whu.edu.cn (WangTong)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://spacetop.win/tags/%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>如何阅读这 50 篇遥感 AI 研究笔记</title><link>https://spacetop.win/2026/06/00-reading-roadmap/</link><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author><name>WangTong</name></author><guid>https://spacetop.win/2026/06/00-reading-roadmap/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="如何阅读这-50-篇遥感-ai-研究笔记" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e9%98%85%e8%af%bb%e8%bf%99-50-%e7%af%87%e9%81%a5%e6%84%9f-ai-%e7%a0%94%e7%a9%b6%e7%ac%94%e8%ae%b0" class="header-mark"></a>如何阅读这 50 篇遥感 AI 研究笔记</h1><p>如果目标是快速找论文题目，优先读 RS-01、RS-06、RS-23、RS-26、RS-31、RS-36、RS-47。它们分别对应 promptable segmentation、证据约束 VQA、可信制图、大图剪枝、谱段适配、raster-vector 融合和 benchmark 去重。</p>
<p>如果目标是写综述，按十个大方向分组阅读。每组 5 篇，刚好形成一个相关工作小节。</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>